{"tid":774067,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Fallout 76》BETA 版和正式版皆不會登錄 STEAM 平台","createTime":"2018-08-10T04:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T02:35:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e0e108c73730a50733eea0575a440c7c3cf867","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/35842/fallout-76-wont-launch-on-steam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F35842%2Ffallout-76-wont-launch-on-steam&d=58LXFaom6tC%2FuxYJ5NNIDsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=8694f294\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/35842/fallout-76-wont-launch-on-steam</a><br />\n<br />\nBethesda 倍受矚目的人氣系列新作《異塵餘生 76》（Fallout 76），預計將於 11 月 14 日正式在 PS4、Xbox One、與 PC 平台發售，只不過這裡的 PC 平台並不代表 Steam。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1729238/org/898b6053ee1eab2c41493052eb2f6a4d.jpg/kpa-rzidKKesSDyHqlIJfrNpHj6-hmS78w9MdvMPTHY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1729238%2Forg%2F898b6053ee1eab2c41493052eb2f6a4d.jpg%2Fkpa-rzidKKesSDyHqlIJfrNpHj6-hmS78w9MdvMPTHY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a5990109&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n <br />\n根據《異塵餘生 76》目前 B.E.T.A. 測試階段的 FAQ 頁面聲明，提到遊戲 PS4、Xbox One、與 PC 平台發售，其中 PC 平台僅標明 <a href=\"http://Bethesda.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBethesda.net&d=58LXFaom6tC%2FuxYJ5NNIDsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=0bf19342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bethesda.net</a> 的啟動器，並未提到 Steam 以及其他 PC 電子平台。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn2-techbang.pixfs.net/system/images/453451/original/9c2bb55e6b823e374df4b8d2c95ea12b.jpg?1533615315\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-techbang.pixfs.net%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F453451%2Foriginal%2F9c2bb55e6b823e374df4b8d2c95ea12b.jpg%3F1533615315&h=a72abb78&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e35792e05e3cee8bcd9c91164e5bbaed38c84112","tid":774067,"uid":38017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98dce7dd29462b2c98662fbce76fa73688162ebf","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"此外，在《異塵餘生 76》官方購買頁面上，平台選項中的 PC 同樣沒有提及 Steam，同時在外媒致信詢問，獲得了官方確切的回答證實：「《異塵餘生 76》PC 版測試或是上市，都只會登上 <a href=\"http://Bethesda.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBethesda.net&d=58LXFaom6tC%2FuxYJ5NNIDsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=0bf19342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bethesda.net</a>，不會在 Steam。」<br />\n <br />\n有鑑於 Bethesda 旗下諸多大作系列如《上古卷軸》、《德軍總部》、以及過去《異塵餘生》系列皆在 Steam 上發布，《異塵餘生 76》選擇只在自家啟動器上發布遊戲，捨棄擁有全球最大 PC 玩家市場的 Steam 算是相當有膽識的作法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fallout.bethesda.net/buy-now\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffallout.bethesda.net%2Fbuy-now&d=58LXFaom6tC%2FuxYJ5NNIDsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=49d8d13e\" target=\"_blank\">https://fallout.bethesda.net/buy-now</a>"},{"pid":"d9c4db2471880c1f7f0b51133cf8be92bc680364","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - Dhhdjdjdjdhdhd )<br />\n完全封鎖"},{"pid":"19dd063c0978e25561ec01140f8d8335c818d368","tid":774067,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"學EA自己起個壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c7f00393d4f840fdfeeb25bfbccf5e1af62f93","tid":774067,"uid":85659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d9c4db2471880c1f7f0b51133cf8be92bc680364","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - Dhhdjdjdjdhdhd )<br />\n完全封鎖"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"2樓UP過乜黎 唔怪得少左層<img s