&h=0bf19342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bethesda.net</a> 帳號，輸入代碼後即可參與。在 PlayStation Store、Xbox One Store 或 <a href=\"http://Bethesda.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBethesda.net&d=58LXFaom6tC%2FuxYJ5NNIDsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=0bf19342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bethesda.net</a> 預購數位版者將自動取得資格。"},{"pid":"993d541a5f5726584b469780027e524d0e32b914","tid":774067,"uid":58931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7c7f00393d4f840fdfeeb25bfbccf5e1af62f93","tid":774067,"uid":85659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d9c4db2471880c1f7f0b51133cf8be92bc680364","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - Dhhdjdjdjdhdhd )<br />\n完全封鎖"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"2樓UP過乜黎 唔怪得少左層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"我都少左層 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b901955fa4b03819b10409de4159b811ddf33d9","tid":774067,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14beffec6ca16186c02c3c40317c4e75521d2946","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7c7f00393d4f840fdfeeb25bfbccf5e1af62f93","tid":774067,"uid":85659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d9c4db2471880c1f7f0b51133cf8be92bc680364","tid":774067,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - Dhhdjdjdjdhdhd )<br />\n完全封鎖"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"2樓UP過乜黎 唔怪得少左層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"開嚟睇吓，咪話我唔益你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" clas